            ("Under Modigliani-Miller (with taxes), the value of a levered firm:", "根據Modigliani-Miller（含稅），有槓桿公司的價值：", ["Exceeds the value of an unlevered firm by the present value of the tax shield", "Equals the unlevered firm value", "Is less than the unlevered firm value", "Is independent of capital structure"], ["超過無槓桿公司的價值，差額為稅盾的現值", "等於無槓桿公司價值", "低於無槓桿公司價值", "與資本結構無關"], 0, "With taxes: VL = VU + PV(tax shield). The tax deductibility of interest creates a tax shield that increases firm value with leverage.", "含稅：VL = VU + PV（稅盾）。利息的稅務扣減創造了稅盾，使公司價值隨槓桿增加。"),
            ("The dividend discount model (DDM) values a share based on:", "股息貼現模型（DDM）基於以下對股份進行估值：", ["The present value of all future expected dividends", "The current share price", "The book value per share", "The company's total assets"], ["所有未來預期股息的現值", "當前股價", "每股賬面價值", "公司總資產"], 0, "DDM: P₀ = Σ(Dt / (1+r)^t). The intrinsic value equals the present value of all expected future dividends, discounted at the required rate of return.", "DDM：P₀ = Σ（Dt /（1+r）^t）。內在價值等於所有預期未來股息的現值，按要求回報率貼現。"),
